And we\\\\'re looking for more people like this to join our friendly and professional team. Crowne Plaza Abu Dhabi is conveniently located in the city centre, minutes away from key business locations, having 236 luxurious rooms, offers an excellent choice of restaurants bars, has 3 function rooms & 3 board rooms equipped with both WiFi & cabled high speed internet access, has got an exciting opportunity for you to join us as one of our Bartender. We have an exciting opportunity for you to join our Food & Beverage team as Bartender . You are under the guidance and supervision of the F&B; Manager and within the limits of established Crowne Plaza Abu Dhabi policies, procedures and F&B;\\\\'s manual. You are also responsible to: clean and prepare bar obtain adequate quantities of stock from the stockrooms as per the request sheet; double check all items received from the stores and ensure this corresponds with the requisition form; have a complete Food and Beverage knowledge of the Menu, Wine list, Cocktail list and any special promotion; and ensure that all information / duties received by the Supervisor or Manager is followed accurately. Ideally, you should be willing to work in shifting schedule and a good team player.
Desired Candidate Profile
